# History Tracking

When modifying files in this workspace, update `.llm/history/active/[feature]/[feature]-part-01.md` (or the latest part file):

```markdown
### Session N - YYYY-MM-DD
#### Prompt (Developer|Agent)
[Exact verbatim prompt]
#### Key Decisions
- Decision 1
#### Files Created/Modified
- path/to/file.ts
```

## 10-Session Limit

Each history file is limited to **10 sessions**. When adding session 11, create a new part file (e.g. `[feature]-part-02.md`).

## File Naming

- `.llm/history/active/[feature]/[feature]-part-01.md` (sessions 1-10)
- `[feature]-part-02.md` (sessions 11-20), etc.

End response with history confirmation. If working on files not matched by the globs above (e.g. `docs/*.md`), still update history when making substantive changes.
